# Color-Splitting

In Color-Split puzzles you will see balls of several colors and exits of the same colors.
The object is to bring the balls to the exits of the same color, but watch out. Any ball getting to the wrong exist will be destroyed.

If you suffer from color-blindness and are therefore unable to tell the colors of the balls and the exits apart, please turn on the color-blind mode in the main config to have the balls and exits marked.